Package eu.acclimatize.unison.location

Interface CoordinatesStore

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeoDBStore, PostGISStore
    public interface CoordinatesStore
    An interface that defines the contract between generic location classes and spatial database specific classes.

      • save

        void save​(double longitude,
          double latitude,
          LocationDetails location)
        Saves the coordinates and location details.
        Parameters:
        longitude - The longitude coordinate.
        latitude - The latitude coordinate.
        location - Generic information, such as the location name, related to the coordinates.

      • sortedFindAll

        java.lang.Iterable<? extends java.lang.Object> sortedFindAll()
        Finds a sorted list of coordinates. The sorting order is determines by the CoordinatesConfig.sort() bean.
        Returns:
        An ordered list of coordinates.
